juniIpProfileAgent.name: juniIpProfileAgent

revisions.description: Added support for Blocking multicast sources on IP Interfaces - rsIpProfileBlockMulticastSources.
Added support for Flow Stats a.k.a. J-Flow for IP Interfaces - rsIpProfileFlowStats.
Added support for IP filter options all for IP Interfaces - rsIpProfileFilterOptionsAll.
Added support for TCP MSS configuration of IP Interfaces - rsIpProfileTcpMss.

Replaced Unisphere names with Juniper names. Obsoleted loopback objects for unnumbered interfaces and added inherited numbered interface objects in juniIpProfileTable (required the addition of juniIpProfileGroup3).
The initial release of this management information module.

juniIpProfileAgent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the IP Profile Manager component of the SNMP agent in the Juniper E-series family of products.

juniIpProfileAgentV1.name: juniIpProfileAgentV1
juniIpProfileAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the IP Profile component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This
        version of the IP Profile Manager component was supported in JUNOSe 1.x
        system releases.
juniIpProfileAgentV1.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the IP Profile Manager application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when the profile loopback object changed.

juniIpProfileAgentV2.name: juniIpProfileAgentV2
juniIpProfileAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the IP Profile component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This
        version of the IP Profile Manager component was supported in JUNOSe 2.x
        system releases.
juniIpProfileAgentV2.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the IP Profile Manager application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when juniIpProfileRowStatus was deprecate and the juniIpProfileSetMap and juniIpProfileSrcAddrValidEnable objects were added.

juniIpProfileAgentV3.name: juniIpProfileAgentV3
juniIpProfileAgentV3.productrelease:
Version 3 of the IP Profile component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This
        version of the IP Profile Manager component was supported in JUNOSe 3.0
        through 4.x system releases.
juniIpProfileAgentV3.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the IP Profile Manager application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when juniIpProfileLoopback was made obsolete and the juniIpProfileInheritNumString object was added.

juniIpProfileAgentV4.name: juniIpProfileAgentV4
juniIpProfileAgentV4.productrelease:
Version 4 of the IP Profile component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This
        version of the IP Profile Manager component was supported in JUNOSe 5.0
        and 5.1 system releases.
juniIpProfileAgentV4.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the IP Profile Manager application in JUNOSe. These capabilities were made obsolete when TCP MSS configuration support for IP Interface was added.

juniIpProfileAgentV5.name: juniIpProfileAgentV5

juniIpProfileAgentV5.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the IP Profile Manager application in JUNOSe.
